Package: gerr
Title: Gene-set Enrichment with Regularized Regression
Version: 0.99.21
Author: Tao Fang and Jitao David Zhang, with inputs from Daniel Marbach
Maintainer: Tao Fang <talonvonfang@gmail.com>
Description: The package implements gene-set enrichment wirh regularized regression. The method can be used to annotate any set of genes of interest with heterogeneous and potentially redundant gene-sets.
Imports: glmnet,
         igraph,
         Matrix,
         utils
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
biocViews: GeneSetEnrichment,Regression,Pathways,GO, Reactome
License: Artistic-2.0
BugReports: https://github.com/TaoDFang/gerr/issues
LazyData: false
Encoding: UTF-8
VignetteBuilder: knitr
